				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\ge$$\end{document} 94%) compared to control subjects. Additionally, it was able to accurately discriminate between progressive MCI and stable MCI (AUC = 78%) during a 3-year follow-up.

