				\begin{document}$$\:1\times\:1$$\end{document}). Figure 4 depicts the Xception model’s architecture and different layers. According to this image, the Xception architecture has three primary components: the entry flow, the middle flow, and the exit flow, with skip connections around the 36 layers52.

